{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515200/extras/store_headline_01_EN_DE.png?t=1737992365\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Chaos at the headquarters of the video game organization, UPIXO: the villain, El Pix, has stolen some important and historically valuable artifacts of video game history from the archive. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Help Chubby retrieve all the artifacts from El Pix's icy realm of Snowdriftland!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515200/extras/store_story.gif?t=1737992365\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515200/extras/store_headline_02_EN.png?t=1737992365\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Mission in Snowdriftland is unique in its concept: Play it like a traditional Advent calendar, and select a level every day and let Chubby guide you through the cold winter days. Or play it like a classic platformer - any time you want.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515200/extras/map.gif?t=1737992365\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515200/extras/store_headline_03_EN.png?t=1737992365\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Mission in Snowdriftland offers the right gaming experience for all players: younger and less experienced gamers can get off to a quick and easy start and jump right in to start searching for the artifacts, while core gamers will face a cool challenge as they collect all 24 snowflakes per level.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515200/extras/store_ingame.gif?t=1737992365\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515200/extras/store_headline_04_EN.png?t=1737992365\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Prepare to confront some wacky enemies like penguins in squirrel costumes, polar bear joggers listening to music, flaming fire bumblebees and many more.<br> <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515200/extras/store_creatures_01.gif?t=1737992365\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515200/extras/store_creatures_02.gif?t=1737992365\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515200/extras/store_headline_05_EN.png?t=1737992365\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Compete against four Minibosses, the subordinates of El Pix, who are standing in your way after every world. Defeat them to prove that you can face the big boss himself! <br> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515200/extras/store_minibosses_01.gif?t=1737992365\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515200/extras/store_minibosses_02.gif?t=1737992365\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515200/extras/store_headline_06_EN.png?t=1737992365\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore Secret Areas containing strange Glitch Pixels in every level. Collect them all to solve the secret behind the odd Pixel Mass found in the newly discovered Hole!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515200/extras/store_secretareas.gif?t=1737992365\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515200/extras/store_headline_07_EN_DE.png?t=1737992365\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">24 levels + huge bonus level + 1 end boss battle</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">4 different worlds</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Mini boss battles in each world</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Secret areas</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Pixel art</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Retro music</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Full controller support</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Speedrun timer </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Achievements<br><br>Coming soon:</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Challenges, Highscore lists and more!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Chubby is on another mission...<i>will you join him?</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515200/extras/pinku_walk.gif?t=1737992365\" /></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Lake Explorer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1515200/96e6414ba4892c1564ad6f752f6c52fc68633cdd.jpg"},{"name":"Forest Explorer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1515200/e034c8eaa5744ebc05fde27f1f3e2b5a1ecf7d27.jpg"},{"name":"Mountain Explorer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1515200/78b0bc84b4bd70ba7a9d9a34359e0dd474bb7460.jpg"},{"name":"Cave Explorer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1515200/3eff924da8d8e9070eec03eaae115d0391dbc5c2.jpg"},{"name":"Heart Container - Lake","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1515200/b0fc279e62e9b57c0778c2ac06eed822d6846005.jpg"},{"name":"Heart Container - Forest","path